				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If a write to $2000 just set bit 7 (when it was clear before) and the VBL flag is already set, an NMI will occur immediately. So the solution is to just clear the VBL flag first, which will have the next NMI occur on the start of the next VBL:
<br />
<br />bit $2002 ; clear VBL flag
<br />lda #$80
<br />sta $2000 ; enable nmi</div>

